  <Docs>
    <summary>Represents options for creating XPS documents.</summary>
    <remarks><format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[
## Remarks

Provides configuration options when creating XPS documents with <xref:M:SkiaSharp.SKDocument.CreateXps*>.

## Examples

```csharp
var options = new SKDocumentXpsOptions
{
    Dpi = 300,
    AllowNoPngs = true,
};
using var doc = SKDocument.CreateXps("/output.xps", options);
```
]]></format></remarks>
